---
title: Rice
cuisine: World
yields: 6
---

Rinse @rice{2%cups}.

Add @water{6%cups} to a #med to large saucepan{} and add the rice.

Turn to high until boiling, then reduce heat to low and put lid on. Set timer for ~{25%minutes}.

Optionally add @salt{dash} and/or @butter{4%tbsp} towards the end of timer.

Fluff with fork & serve!
